OL,3,C'Tied up with cable ties' and
OL,4,C'stabbing threats': Retail staff
OL,5,Creveal violence they face in store
OL,7,FFor a long time now, shop workers
OL,8,Fhave been at the receiving end of
OL,9,Fviolence, intimidation, and
OL,10,Faggression while trying to do their
OL,11,Fjob.
OL,13,FBut as the shoplifting crisis spirals
OL,14,Fso does the threat they face - but
OL,15,Fwhat's being done about it?
OL,17,FNew figures given to ITV News by the
OL,18,Fshop workers union USDAW show half of
OL,19,Fretail staff have no confidence that
OL,20,Freporting violent abuse to the police
OL,21,Fwill make a difference.
